{"results":[{"aya":"015","id":5863,"locale":"zh","sura":"083","text":"真的，在那日，他们必受阻拦，不得觐见他们的主。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"016","id":5864,"locale":"zh","sura":"083","text":"然後，他们必堕入烈火之中。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"017","id":5865,"locale":"zh","sura":"083","text":"然後，或者将对他们说：这就是你们所否认的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"018","id":5866,"locale":"zh","sura":"083","text":"真的，善人们的记录，确在善行簿中。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"019","id":5867,"locale":"zh","sura":"083","text":"你怎能知道善行簿是什麽？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"020","id":5868,"locale":"zh","sura":"083","text":"是一本封存的簿子，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"021","id":5869,"locale":"zh","sura":"083","text":"真主所亲近的天神们将作证它。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":6,"previousPage":"/zh/s083-2.json","nextPage":"/zh/s083-4.json"}}